{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"547872b513","title":"中共中山大学委员会关于错划汪廷奎为右派分子改正通知书","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56a337f413","index":0,"year":1979,"month":3,"day":12,"articleId":"547872b513"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac242afeb9","type":"title","text":"中共中山大学委员会关于错划汪廷奎为右派分子改正通知书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"},{"id":"7b0a591866","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央〔1978〕55号文件指示，我们对汪廷奎同志1958年3月被划为右派分子进行了复查，认为属于错划，决定给予改正，恢复政治名誉，并作如下安排处理：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"},{"id":"297dff4e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）按中央五部〔79〕143号文件规定，由本人现所在地区县以上组织、人事、劳动部门分配适当工作，工龄从离校之日起计算。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"},{"id":"0e30302985","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）工资问题按中央规定执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"},{"id":"88d266e5dc","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中山大学委员会一九七九年三月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"},{"id":"8fc8304a93","type":"appellation","text":"来源：汪廷奎《“左”氏春秋自纪》，汪廷奎提供。汪廷奎：1957年时为中山大学历史系学生。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513"}],"page":{"id":"067f2a1231","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"547872b513","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}